scripts.build: yarn babel:build:clean && yarn babel:build::cjs && yarn babel:build::esm && yarn tsc:build::types && yarn hack:update-package-exports
scripts.cmd:jest: cd $INIT_CWD && yarn cmd:node --disable-warning=ExperimentalWarning --experimental-vm-modules $(yarn workspace @holypack/integration-jest bin jest)
scripts.cmd:jest::expose-gc: cd $INIT_CWD && yarn cmd:node --disable-warning=ExperimentalWarning --experimental-vm-modules --expose-gc --no-compilation-cache $(yarn workspace @holypack/integration-jest bin jest)
